# CODEOWNERS for the ACG Rubric
#
# Every PR requires review from the owners of the paths it touches.
# The list below is intentionally minimal; add owners as the project grows.

# Repository-wide default
*                               @acg-rubric/maintainers

# Rubric substance — additional review required
/rubric/                        @acg-rubric/maintainers @acg-rubric/rubric-editors
/rubric/thresholds.md           @acg-rubric/maintainers
/rubric/criteria/               @acg-rubric/rubric-editors

# Badge and governance — highest sensitivity
/badge/expiry-and-revocation.md @acg-rubric/maintainers
/badge/register.md              @acg-rubric/maintainers
/GOVERNANCE.md                  @acg-rubric/maintainers

# Mappings — cross-framework knowledge
/mappings/                      @acg-rubric/mapping-owners

# Evidence — sanitization gate
/evidence/                      @acg-rubric/evidence-reviewers
